1
00:01:05,792 --> 00:01:08,416
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,416 --> 00:01:11,328
=Episode 5=

3
00:01:11,328 --> 00:01:13,719
(Star-Gazing Pavilion)

4
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:16,864
So, our bodies swapped

5
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,920
because Dada's witchcraft
was used on us?

6
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:22,079
You never know what will happen.

7
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,680
According to this ancient book,

8
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:27,599
this witchcraft is used
only to kill people involved.

9
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,040
Rarely does it go awry.

10
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:33,079
But your yin-yang reversal
caused the swap.

11
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:38,200
Pity we only found the first volume.

12
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,159
It only records
how to cast this witchcraft.

13
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:43,200
To lift it, we need to find
the second volume.

14
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:46,200
Don't tell me we have to go to Dada.

15
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,719
I have a way to search for it.

16
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,579
But before that,

17
00:01:50,579 --> 00:01:54,120
both of you have to endure this
for a while longer.

18
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:59,719
Who is the caster's target, me or you?

19
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:02,760
We have to do something.

20
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:05,120
As long as we pretend to be fine,

21
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,840
the caster will think
their scheme remains hidden.

22
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:11,240
Once we find the second volume,
I'll slowly reel the caster in.

23
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:14,000
With the war ongoing,
we can't afford more chaos.

24
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,439
You're so thoughtful.

25
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,400
I'm eager to see
what tricks they'll pull.

26
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:24,400
Are you talking about me?

27
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,000
What did I miss? Looks like a nice chat.

28
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,400
Why not share it with me?

29
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:38,199
We were talking about an ancient book.

30
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,400
You want it?

31
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,280
Well, if you want it,

32
00:02:42,439 --> 00:02:45,120
as your adorable brother,
I'll personally get it for you.

33
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:48,400
But my power alone is limited.

34
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:51,264
Can I look for it outside

35
00:02:51,264 --> 00:02:53,199
with the Grand Preceptor?

36
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,560
I think you want
to corrupt the Grand Preceptor.

37
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,439
Jinyun.

38
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,960
Please, Jinyun.

39
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,759
Allow me to tell a fortune
for Your Highness.

40
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,360
On wealth?

41
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,080
On romance.

42
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,800
No.

43
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:11,080
I have my brother, my mother, and money.

44
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,039
That's all I want.

45
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,759
Our plan failed.

46
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:19,479
Who'd have thought
that an uneducated Empress

47
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,319
would see through our scheme?

48
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,599
The Empress is a remarkable woman.

49
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:28,879
I'd be disappointed if she hadn't.

50
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,479
Sadly, you lost a key pawn for nothing.

51
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:35,159
Isn't that a pity?

52
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,960
If not for our grand plan,

53
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:42,759
why would I
make a distant relative my niece?

54
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:47,840
Who knew the fool would use an heir
to replace the current Empress?

55
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,439
Utterly useless.

56
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,560
Don't worry.

57
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:55,039
As long as we're players in this game,

58
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:58,199
I can revive even the dead.

59
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,000
Let me see.

60
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,720
How could you be so careless?

61
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:22,000
You kept staring at me!
How could I concentrate?

62
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:27,000
If you weren't looking at me,
how'd you know I was watching?

63
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:27,879
You...

64
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,040
Report!

65
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:38,920
Your Majesty,
General Xu Jun returned gravely wounded!

66
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,959
Like my father, he never leaves
the battle for minor wounds.

67
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:51,399
As he returned,
he must be critically injured.

68
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,560
I'm going to see him!

69
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,800
Xu Yu, you can't.

70
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:56,399
As the Emperor, it's inappropriate.

71
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,800
I'll go instead.

72
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,439
But...

73
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:01,160
Xu Jun is also my brother by right.

74
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:11,199
You're injured. Skip the formalities.

75
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,839
That's inappropriate.

76
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:15,600
Greetings, Your Grace.

77
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:20,079
How were you so badly wounded?

78
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,560
No worries.

79
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,959
I'm quite fine.

80
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:29,120
Is the northern front stable?

81
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,639
Why did I get no messages
from you for so long?

82
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:35,879
A subject must hold his tongue.
Contacting the harem is overstepping.

83
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:39,639
Don't worry.
I'm glad to fight alongside Father.

84
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:42,439
But you're alone in the harem.

85
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,439
You're suffering a lot, aren't you?

86
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:51,720
Duo.

87
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,639
Xu Duo!

88
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,839
Why won't you call me Duo?

89
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,040
Duo.

90
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:03,959
Come! You rarely came back. Let me see

91
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:05,480
if you've neglected your training.

92
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:14,759
Duo.

93
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:22,400
I've been unwell lately.

94
00:06:22,912 --> 00:06:24,920
Yu, what's wrong with you?

95
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:28,000
Are you alright? What's wrong?

96
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:28,879
I'm pregnant.

97
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:35,319
So, I'm going to be an uncle!

98
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,879
If it's a boy,
I'll teach him martial arts.

99
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,600
I'll make him the world's best!

100
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,480
If it is a boy,

101
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:46,240
he will be the imperial heir,

102
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:48,000
destined to be Crown Prince!

103
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,560
No need for you to teach.

104
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,000
It is very necessary.

105
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:53,800
His Majesty doesn't know martial arts.

106
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,639
That's why military power gets divided
among those old men.

107
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:57,160
Duo.

108
00:06:58,399 --> 00:07:01,000
That's such a hurtful thing to say.

109
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,759
Yu.

110
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:02,680
Jun.

111
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,199
Jun.

112
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:11,199
I'm often away leading troops,
but I'm not foolish.

113
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,160
Your pregnancy should be joyous.

114
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:17,439
But the harem is even more dangerous
than the battlefield.

115
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,720
Moreover, His Majesty doesn't favor you.

116
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:25,600
From now on, act with extreme caution.
Don't bring trouble upon yourself.

117
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:31,120
(Is it well known
that I don't favor Xu Yu?)

118
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:35,680
As long as you're discreet, modest,
and don't oppose His Majesty,

119
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:38,879
you and your child, even if unfavored,

120
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:42,759
will be protected
by our family for life.

121
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:47,560
I've heard that the Marquis of Zhenbei
is acting suspiciously.

122
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:50,480
He may attempt to harm His Majesty
during the autumn hunt.

123
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,672
When you return to the palace,
warn His Majesty

124
00:07:52,672 --> 00:07:55,639
to stay vigilant
and not to fall into his trap.

125
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:59,519
Duo, aren't you worried about me?

126
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:01,199
Their target is His Majesty.

127
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:05,240
Besides, as subjects,
we're loyal to our sovereign.

128
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:07,480
Father taught us that.

129
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:14,360
(Knowing I don't favor Xu Yu,
they remain loyal to the sovereign.)

130
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:23,480
Xiao Jinyun is too weak.
He needs to exercise more.

131
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:26,680
Your Majesty.

132
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,600
Who are you calling weak?

133
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:30,279
How is my big brother?

134
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,000
He's fine.

135
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:36,039
Did you ask about my father and Duo?

136
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,120
They're well too.

137
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:41,519
They're just worried
about you suffering here.

138
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:46,159
Don't worry. You've been good lately.

139
00:08:48,639 --> 00:08:50,639
Your Majesty, what happened to your arm?

140
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:54,159
It's nothing. Duo just patted me.

141
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,919
And then he shook me
until my head nearly came off.

142
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,559
He even wanted to spar.

143
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,200
Didn't you give yourself away?

144
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:06,120
I was clever enough
to claim you're pregnant.

145
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,240
Naturally, he couldn't force me
to spar again.

146
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,519
Pregnant?

147
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,279
Your Majesty, how could you say that?

148
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:15,159
If they believe it,
where will I get a child?

149
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:20,080
Then let's actually have one.

150
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,320
Your Majesty.

151
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:41,840
Soft armor?
This is great protective gear.

152
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,039
Jun gave this to you?

153
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:45,720
Actually, your father let Jun
give it to you.

154
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,399
They all care about you.

155
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,600
I also miss my father.

156
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:58,480
By the way,
Duo mentioned something else.

157
00:09:58,799 --> 00:10:00,039
The autumn hunt is coming up.

158
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,000
Autumn hunt?

159
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,559
So I can ride horses?

160
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:08,080
Sure. Since you're using my body now,

161
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,759
you can hunt freely and enjoy yourself.

162
00:10:12,608 --> 00:10:13,639
No, wait.

163
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,360
You are too weak.

164
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:20,080
To avoid embarrassing myself,
I have to practice riding and archery.

165
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,519
Someone! Prepare my horse.

166
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:30,039
Who are you calling weak? You...

167
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,639
So heavy.

168
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:41,679
(Hunting Ground)
It's time.

169
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,759
Your Majesty,
please commence the autumn hunt.

170
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:02,624
Since it's an autumn hunt,
we should pursue live prey.

171
00:11:03,009 --> 00:11:06,360
It's the same as the archery targets
on the training field, isn't it?

172
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:11,240
Your Majesty, your safety matters.
You can't be too careful.

173
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,159
Release it.

174
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,240
Yes.

175
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,720
We've never heard of Your Majesty
practicing riding or archery.

176
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,039
What if...

177
00:11:24,399 --> 00:11:27,120
What? You doubt me?

178
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:28,600
I wouldn't dare.

179
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,639
Prince Ning can't come due to illness.

180
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,512
He privately instructed me

181
00:11:32,512 --> 00:11:34,399
to protect Your Majesty.

182
00:11:34,519 --> 00:11:35,879
Please think twice, Your Majesty.

183
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:38,279
My decision is final. No more words.

184
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:42,360
- May Your Majesty have swift victory.
- May Your Majesty have swift victory.

185
00:11:57,568 --> 00:11:58,240
Giddy up!

186
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:00,559
Giddy up!

187
00:12:07,648 --> 00:12:08,200
Giddy up!

188
00:12:13,312 --> 00:12:13,919
Giddy up!

189
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,240
Giddy up!

190
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:31,424
♪Parting clouds to get the waxing moon♪

191
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:36,723
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

192
00:13:38,048 --> 00:13:43,463
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

193
00:13:44,032 --> 00:13:48,576
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

194
00:13:49,216 --> 00:13:54,480
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

195
00:13:54,848 --> 00:14:00,525
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

196
00:14:00,864 --> 00:14:02,880
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

197
00:14:03,072 --> 00:14:06,816
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

198
00:14:07,392 --> 00:14:12,064
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

199
00:14:12,608 --> 00:14:14,368
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

200
00:14:14,688 --> 00:14:18,304
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

201
00:14:18,551 --> 00:14:24,078
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
